description: Undocumented RMF element <hbar> progress/loading bar (invisible when zero)
---

Horizontal progress bar used for loading UI. Typical form:
```text
<hbar BACKGROUND BAR_ITEM cvar PROGRESS_CVAR invisible>
```
- `BACKGROUND` — background image key
- `BAR_ITEM` — bar/segment image key
- `cvar <name>` — progress cvar expected to go from 0 -> 1
- `invisible` — hide object when progress is 0

